text:
From the VA to the USDA to the FAA, my office has heard from countless dedicated federal employees who have been laid off.

Whether they've worked for one year or more than a decade, these public servants have worked tirelessly for the American people without a single bad mark. Some even spent years serving in our nation's military. Now, they have been let go without cause.

@HouseDemocrats will stand with them because they deserve better.
